Flask-Mailer
============

A Flask extension for sending email messages with pluggable backends
and pythonic API.

Contributing
------------

Don't hesitate to create a `GitHub issue
<https://github.com/vitalk/flask-mailer/issues>`_ for any **bug** or
**suggestion**.



